-- This is auto-generated code
--ALTER VIEW dbo.vw_lms_dbocustomer
--AS
SELECT
    R.*
    ,S.Latest_Lat
    ,S.Latest_Lng
    ,S.Latest_TAT
    ,S.MODE_Count
    ,S.Mode_Lat
    ,S.Mode_Lng
    ,S.Mode_TAT
    ,S.AVG_DROP_TAT
    ,S.STDEV_DROP_TAT
    ,S.NUM_ROWS_TOTAL
FROM
    OPENROWSET(BULK 'https://citylogisticsstorage.dfs.core.windows.net/synapse/DataLake Dev/CTS/MasterData/lms_dbocustomer.parquet/**',FORMAT = 'PARQUET') AS R
    LEFT JOIN OPENROWSET(BULK 'https://citylogisticsstorage.dfs.core.windows.net/synapse/DataLake Dev/CTS/MasterData/lms_customer_dispatchsegment_calc.parquet/**',FORMAT = 'PARQUET') AS S
        ON R.ID = S.lms_waybill_delivercustid
